Evelyn Avenue, Sunnyvale CA 94086', 'show contact info', 'https://essexapts.info/Windsor-Ridge', 'Minutes from historic downtown Sunnyvale, CA, Windsor Ridge apartment homes offer an inviting park-like enclave at a convenient Silicon Valley location ❤', 'Apartment 510', 'Rent.... $3249 on a 13 month lease!', 'Deposit.... $600 Security Deposit (on approved credit)', 'Bedrooms.... 2 bedroom', 'Bathrooms... 1 bathroom', 'Sq.', 'Feet.... 900', 'Our community is in a prime position for zipping all around the Bay Area.', 'The VTA light rail station and the Sunnyvale Caltrain Station are each within a few miles of your front door, and highways 101 and 237 are also within easy reach.', 'If you work for one of the many surrounding tech giants, you’ll also have curbside access to commuter shuttles to and from companies like Apple, Google, and Facebook!', '🏢', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change without notice.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.']
